106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=RYCS1wTE014Q7kNvgH90fEC&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A_SlcNshn6B2FrZRPif1eDK&oh=00_AYANJUrO-8RF4JKmqDc9GRsgb4RtbutA3Pj3B_q7XyznWQ&oe=66EAB073"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "file (33).png", "id": "1623171634894204", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75451785_1623171638227537_7743361280080950072_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i8HZkLF3mj4Q7kNvgEvRK3S&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A_SlcNshn6B2FrZRPif1eDK&oh=00_AYAqgqng0GVxHiFFa-DbGLHWeQhYVFS-ANg7gPQkPr0e3Q&oe=66EAA534"}, "display_name": "MasterRunners", "keywords": ["runners", "master", "mrvr", "mrvrv2", "masterunner"], "long_description": "# Welcome to the MasterRunners Page.\n\nMasterRunners is a free-to-play multiplayer hand based movement game surrounding a variety of entertaining gamemodes, cosmetics, obstacles, etc.\n\nWith over **9+ gamemodes** and an **active player count of 100,000+**, we guarantee this game is worth your time. We have lots to offer, so what are you waiting for!?\n\n# What you can do:\n\n- Play Gamemodes with players across the **WORLD**. MasterRunners can be played worldwide and with our **advanced multiplayer system**, you can enjoy multiplayer & have a very fun time. For the gamemodes, we build special gamemodes that have never been used in others games making us stand out and more fun.\n{440204882312445}\n- Chill with friends and have a **great time.** With areas such as the \"Main Hub\", you can relax and have a calming time with buddies as you talk to your hearts desire.\n{509486194868299}\n- Shop for new cosmetics at Gregson's Shop with the free in-game currency... Energy! Using energy, you can get all kinds of cosmetics of any type just with one click. This is how you can customize your character!\n{1216230166051298}\n\n- **Survive Monsters..**\n{770419325031966}\n\nAnd more. \n\nThere is lots to do in MasterRunners, so check it out **TODAY!**\n{346841078359419}